Defendant Mike Cartagena in court.  Kristi J Gordon appeared for the State of Wisconsin..  The Defendant files the waiver of attorney form and wants to proceed to dispose of the case today.  The Defendant is sworn in and questioned by the Court.  The Court finds the Defendant is competent to represent himself and to proceed without counsel.   Defendant enters a guilty plea to Count  1.  Court finds defendant guilty.     The Defendant is sentenced as follows:
FINE $379.00 (to be paid at $25.00 per month commencing 12/15/15, 12 days jail as penalty for failure pay;
DNA SURCHARGE: $200.00 (to be paid at $25.00 per month commencing 12/15/15)
  Defendant to provide DNA sample, if not yet provided,   immediately if in custody otherwise within (3) business days at the Waukesha County Sheriff Department.
RESTITUTION: $90.00 (payable to Stephanie D.) (Restitution to be paid prior to court costs);
Defendant is ordered to have no contact with the victim.
